Interact daily with Clients fulfilling count requests, processing email orders, and supporting the Account Management team. The individual has excellent writing, interpersonal and oral communication skills, has an aptitude for marketing concepts, and has a basic understanding of internet advertising.

This is an individual who is organized and able to manage a number of tasks throughout the workday and to meet deadlines and follow up on Client requests.

Proficiency in all Microsoft Office applications is required, as is the willingness and ability to master new applications to fulfill job requirements and to perform other duties as assigned.

As part of the Account Management team, the Marketing Sales Support Specialist is focused on meeting identical objectives: growing revenue and profit for the Company through effective customer sales support and client satisfaction.
